am\": \"the opening\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This cannot be allowed to stand,\\\" said Banka, who warned that if U.S. authorities assert jurisdiction over cases that have nothing to do with them, it risks putting the U.S. outside the global anti-doping system.\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3974, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3801, \"end\": 3806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangka_Island\", \"score\": 0.7916652896664448, \"rank\": 0.2631594561444039, \"text\": \"Banka\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangka_Island\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangka_Island\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"U.S. authorities\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 3843}, {\"ngram\": \"jurisdiction\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3863}, {\"ngram\": \"cases\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3874}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 3892}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3935}, {\"ngram\": \"the global anti-doping system\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Banka also criticized the United States for politicizing anti-doping and called it hypocritical and double standard in a statement published on WADA's official website on June 26.\", \"from\": 3976, \"to\": 4155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3976, \"end\": 3981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangka_Island\", \"score\": 0.7916652896664448, \"rank\": 0.2631594561444039, \"text\": \"Banka\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangka_Island\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangka_Island\"}, {\"begin\": 4002, \"end\": 4015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9995031829718085, \"rank\": 0.0004970639687097287, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbped